comment: Hello! Thank you for another lovely video Thank you for the English subtitles  We spend a lot of time out and about on the weekends and stylish sneakers are a must for me. Seems LAR are not available in US. Last year I purchased Veja sneakers, which are aslo made from recycled leather and eco friendly materials. I’m drawn to responsible companies and better for the environment products. Another sneaker company that makes simple, unbranded sneakers is Thursday Boot Company (high quality, reasonable prices). Love your styling videos, keep them coming!
